<paragraph base="F32570946" id="IFRS09_B3.2.11" principles="no"><paranum>B3.2.11</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 9"/><data name="paranum" value="B3.2.11"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS09_P0828">When measuring the fair values of the part that continues to be recognised and the part that is derecognised for the purposes of applying <xref base="F41907334" href="IFRS09_3.2.13.dita#IFRS09_3.2.13" id="IFRS09_X1101">paragraph 3.2.13</xref>, an entity applies the fair value measurement requirements in <xref base="F41907363" href="../ifrs13/IFRS13_TOC.dita#IFRS13_TOC0001" id="IFRS09_X1102">IFRS 13 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Fair Value Measurement</ph></ph></xref> in addition to <xref base="F41907364" id="IFRS09_X1103" keyref="IFRS09_3.2.14">paragraph 3.2.14</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>